10: In high spirits today too, I see.
13:
We went and invited new audience
members! It'd be strange if I wasn't
excited.
15:
We can't go and give them a
half-hearted performance, so we've
gotta give it our all. No, even better
than our all!
19:
As long as you don't overdo it, that's
fine! Either way, you're looking good.
Keep it up.
23:
I always look good. I'm an idol, after
all!
28:
Wow! Look at all the humans! And all
the bright lights!
31: I can't wait to hear Ai sing!
35:
Yep. The concert will be starting
soon!
49:
Thank you so much for coming out
to our concert today!
53:
Wow, there are a lot of new faces in
the crowd today!
56:
You know... Everyone who came out
today is really lucky!
61:
Today's concert is... a very special
one! How is it special? Can you
guess?
63:
You two are even cuter than usual
today!
66:
Hmm, that makes it sound like we
weren't that cute before⁠—and we
definitely were! No more talk like
that, if you please!
69:
Anyway, where was I... Right! So
today, we don't have a set list!
72:
We're going entirely off of YOUR
energy today!
75:
So, what song are we gonna start off
with?
84:
That was a fast request, wow! Okay,
here we go!
89:
Wow! Such a great sound! Nice
beat! Cool moves!
92:
Incredible. They really are
performing even better than usual.
They're practically glowing.
99:
To think this, too, was a world utterly
unknown to me until now...
103:
All right, what song do you want to
hear next? Keep the requests
coming!
111:
Okay! Don't worry, we'll get through
every single one of your requests
one by one!
118:
I had so much fun! Ai and Saki are
amazing!
122:
Thank you! I'm glad that you
enjoyed our concert.
126:
I have to say, I really didn't expect
you to do a concert without a set
list! That was quite the decision.
130:
You coulda given me some warning.
I had to do like a dozen songs on the
fly there! It wasn't easy.
133:
We always perform that many
songs! And besides, it's not like you
don't know them all!
137:
I hope that all your fears and
misgivings have been cleared up,
now that you've seen the smiles on
your fans' faces.
141:
Idols need to grow along with their
fans. I thought I had understood that
before, but...
142:
I focused too much on creating the
perfect performance and
overlooked what it was the fans truly
wanted. I was... off in my approach.
145:
I'm glad that traveling to other
worlds allowed you to make this
realization.
149:
Instead of endlessly wondering what
song the audience wants to hear, it's
faster and easier to just ask them
directly!
154:
I don't wanna say I told you so, but... I
told you so! Don't sweat the details.
157:
Focusing too much on perfection
isn't always the right call. You've
learned that lesson now, hopefully.
160:
Yes. But that doesn't change the
fact that you're still too careless and
sloppy sometimes.
162:
If you really want to be our leader,
you have to get your act together!
And behave in a manner more
befitting a proper idol!
